      <T n="text">0xCCB10662<!--String: "Welcome to <i>The Sims™ 4 Royalty & Legacy</i>! This pack is all about  <b><font color='#199C2C'>discovery, storytelling and legacy building</font></b>.\n\nExplore the world of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Ondarion</font></b> and experience storybook moments – like Dueling with swords or kissing frogs – in the process of climbing the royal ranks of Nobility.\n\nNoble or not, anyone can start a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty</font></b> to grow their family's influence! Reap the perks of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Prestige</font></b> while maintaining <b><font color='#199C2C'>Unity</font></b>, or embrace the drama of family friction.\n\nAny rise to power risks a fall from grace: beware of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Scandals</font></b>, like <b><font color='#199C2C'>forbidden romances</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>secret children</font></b>! Start a legacy, carve your own regal path, and rise to glory."--></T>
